TEMPEST Products
TEMPEST Laptops | TEMPEST Thin Clients | TEMPEST Workstations | TEMPEST/TSG Accredited Phones | TEMPEST Printers | TEMPEST Video Conferencing


TEMPEST and Zone products are commercial products that have been modified to meet rigorous U.S. Government and NATO (AMSG) specifications for mitigating electro-magnetic emanations, as well as providing protection of sensitive electronic information. Each of our products are certified to NSTISSAM TEMPEST/1-92 Level I and NATO SDIP-27 A standards.
TEMPEST Products



SECURE Products
TSG Accredited Phones | Secure Tablets | Multi Domain Solutions | Limited Range Secure Wireless Access Points


 With the popularity of technologies such as tablets and wireless access points, the Intelligence Community (IC) has expressed considerable interest in implementing these technologies within their secure work spaces. Advanced Programs, Inc. is on the forefront of confronting the challenges the IC faces regarding the security of these mobile solutions by way of physical modification.
Secure Products



TEST Services
TEMPEST Testing | EMI & EMC Testing | Design Support | Production Support | Compliance Testing | NSTISSAM TEMPEST/1-92 | MIL-STD 461 | NSTISSAM TEMPEST/2-95


Assessing the electro-magnetic emanations or susceptibly of systems and products is a crucial information assurance measure requiring sophisticated testing and the right expertise. Advanced Programs, Inc. provides the expertise and the ability to test electro-magnetic emanations for systems and products.
