TEST Services
Assessing the electro-magnetic emanations or susceptibility of systems and products is a crucial information assurance measure requiring sophisticated test equipment and certified expertise. Advanced Programs, Incorporated provides the expertise and the ability to test electro-magnetic emanations for systems and products, and offers a myriad of classified and unclassified compliance assessment services. API utilizes 16 test chambers and employs over 20 certified TEMPEST professionals that can test to standards areas such as NSTISSAM TEMPEST 1-92 and various others. Click below to learn more about our full suite of Cyber Assurance Services.



