 About L3












Headquartered  in New York City, L3 employs approximately 38,000 people worldwide and is a  leading provider of a broad range of communication and electronic systems and  products used on military and commercial platforms. L3 is also a prime  contractor in aerospace systems. The company reported 2015 sales of $10.5  billion.












 





