            Business Description
        



L-3 Advanced Programs is located in Burlington, Massachusetts. This organization primarily operates in the Engineering Services business / industry within the Engineering, Accounting, Research, and Management Services sector. This organization has been operating for approximately 9 years. L-3 Advanced Programs is estimated to generate $7.1 million in annual revenues, and employs approximately 55 people at this single location.









